Package com.buffettinc.hrms.model.time

Class Timesheet

java.lang.Object
com.buffettinc.hrms.model.time.Timesheet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Timesheet extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents a Timesheet to be used by Employee of Buffett Inc. Each timesheet consists of a reference to the Employee with their employeeID, the pay period start date, end date, a list of ShiftEntries representing individual ShiftEntry by a single Employee, whether the Timesheet was approved, and a reference of the approver.
